{"tid":2035082,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"海軍測試激光炮 擊落無人機","createTime":"2020-05-25T15:51:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-26T05:13:56.000Z","uid":2104,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e99a50d4826410219f76b812d362d844c2469cad","tid":2035082,"uid":2104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T15:51:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RaEfuL8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRaEfuL8.jpg&h=2ef1d2af&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GH0BYEx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGH0BYEx.jpg&h=a2f85cea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/64dLRZy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F64dLRZy.jpg&h=dfeef71a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隨著科技的迅速發展，近年各國的軍方亦正試圖研發不同新武器以加強國防。而在近日，美國的兩棲艦「波特蘭號」（LPD-27）就首次在海上為船上安裝的激光武器系統進行測試，並成功利用激光技術系統 (SSL-TM) 擊落了一架無人機，向外界展示其威力。<br />\n<br />\n美國太平洋艦隊在日前於網上發放了一條影片，當中介紹了兩棲艦「波特蘭號」在 5 月 16 日於夏威夷珍珠港附近測試激光武器的威力。從官方所發放的影片中可見，船隻在鎖定無人機並發射激光約 3秒後，該無人機便冒煙並燃燒。美軍就表示該激光系統不一定是為了摧毀目標而使用，而是而破壞對方為首要目的。<br />\n <br />\n「波特蘭號」號艦長 Karrey Sanders 在接受採訪時就表示，通過是次對無人機的試驗將為未來的武器系統奠下基礎，並將重新定義海上戰爭，同是向外界展示出該系統的威力。他亦透露目前美國海軍正研發一種名為 ODIN 的武器，以向飛機發射耀眼的光芒警告對方立即離開，藉此提升國防系統。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xP94wR-wq4g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxP94wR-wq4g&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY6%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=b37ff200\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xP94wR-wq4g</a><br />\n<br />\n引自<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/05/25/uss-portland-fires-laser-weapon-downs-drone-in-first-at-sea-test/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F05%2F25%2Fuss-portland-fires-laser-weapon-downs-drone-in-first-at-sea-test%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=tjA1itiRAyOaH4WNB6QjY6%2BgbAIUXjhk7Wr4LW24j58%3D&h=c7867207\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/05/25/uss-portland-fires-laser-weapon-downs-drone-in-first-at-sea-test/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"b774beba1f5b7bac7dcb69fa20e5dfbfe7e2f451","tid":2035082,"uid":320339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-25T16:21:35.000Z","msg":"唔知北京嘅霧霾擋唔擋得住美國嘅激光呢?<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25fa6cb816c4e5887f3d07d897b7c3035e95d850","tid":2035082,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T05:13:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好似主要對付無人機<br />\n導彈就功率未過"}]}